tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE InfluencerPartnerships (
  partnership_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  influencer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  brand_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  communication_history TEXT,
  contract_details JSON
)

CREATE TABLE Partnerships (
    partnership_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id INT,
    partner_name VARCHAR(255),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE CommunicationHistory (
    communication_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_id INT,
    communication_date DATETIME,
    communication_type VARCHAR(50),
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Partnerships (
    partnership_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_name VARCHAR(50),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE CommunicationHistory (
    communication_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_id INT,
    date_time DATETIME,
    communication_type VARCHAR(50),
    details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE ContractDetails (
    contract_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_id INT,
    contract_type VARCHAR(50),
    contract_terms TEXT,
    amount DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE Influencers (
    influencer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    influencer_email VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    followers_count INT,
    partnership_start_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE Brands (
    brand_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    brand_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    industry VARCHAR(50),
    brand_email VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    contact_person VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE PartnershipContracts (
    contract_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id UUID,
    brand_id UUID,
    contract_date DATE,
    contract_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    contract_duration_months INT
);

CREATE TABLE CommunicationHistory (
    history_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    contract_id UUID,
    communication_date TIMESTAMP,
    communication_type VARCHAR(50),
    communication_details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE PaymentHistory (
    payment_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    contract_id UUID,
    payment_date DATE,
    payment_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    payment_method VARCHAR(50)
);
